  "body": "<center>\n<strong>\n\n<h1>\n  The resource pack can use a this DDM\n  </a> \n  or vanilla theme\n</h1>\n\n<p>\n This pack that adds a cat lying on a shelf to the inventory.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n The cat changes depending on the biome you are in.\n</p>\n \n<p> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/UkMb9QdcPq\">\n  <img\nsrc=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2d383d1a4f89412fcdbeb089b2038e04f2a969e9.png\"  width=\"120\">\n</a>\n</p>\n\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://optifine.net/downloads\">\n  <img\nsrc=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a3f0e934f6ae489f460519f5adbade883c317d76.png\"  width=\"448\">\n</a>\n</p>\n\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://discordapp.com/users/497026487699111938/\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5a766a3c53272231bc64757c9ddc4055163839cf.png\"  width=\"120\">\n</a>\n</p>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9a3d98fc249e2ad2943490be76f9f381c0259eb9.png\" width=\"812\">\n\n<hr>\n\n\n<p>\n  Many thanks to\n  <a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/animated-fox-guis-1-16-x\">Ekuzen\n</a> \nfor providing the idea and some of the textures used in this resourcepack.\n</p>\n  \n<p>\nAlso, special thanks to my friend Kudryavyy for his help in creating textures\n</p>\n\n\n<hr>\n\n![normal](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f519f1806e7c6e9d54499af0af5d717c63a98dc5_0.webp)\n\n![normal vanilla](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/979dbb6c58016c4cd1e9e17b54bcec9153af24c3_0.webp)\n</strong>\n</center>",
